{"tid":1370261,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"GodBlessHK請公開眾籌用途","createTime":"2019-07-27T02:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T17:48:50.000Z","uid":119458,"like":97,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"22d4d3c4ed6a639de72dfc51b3a0bec88e9f1120","tid":1370261,"uid":119458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:47:01.000Z","msg":"捐錢唔係問題，麻煩你地回應返啲錢既用途。<br />\nIG、FB、連登，都有人問過，但遲遲未見你地回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n詳見<br />\n<br />\n急！要人幫手！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1367807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1367807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">G20國圖</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cYsJafX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcYsJafX.png&h=a62c46d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣設計</span></span><br />\nGodBlessHK有大量非原創(公海)文宣，請問你地係唔係可以幫手捐錢畀各文宣組/獨立文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小妹好想支持佢地，但佢地大多匿名又唔收錢，淨係叫大家代佢地上場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">實地採訪</span><br />\n</span>失敬失敬，原來你地團隊有記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知小妹能唔能夠一睹你地既採訪片段，學習學習<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">印刷、戶外宣傳</span></span><br />\n小妹收到既傳單，以及路過既放映會，好似都唔見有你地GodBlessHK既大名。如果想直接捐印刷好既傳單海報/借出器材/送水送野食，請問應該去邊到搵你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n補圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q6wFcu3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ6wFcu3.png&h=d032727f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c5d9fc36ef37210ae4ab844e3d7e0836262d6b04","tid":1370261,"uid":119458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27